---

!! Local LLM

; Base URL
: <$edit-text tiddler="$:/plugins/NoteStreams/WikiSage/local-llm-url" tag="input" default="" placeholder="e.g. http://192.168.86.81:11434" />
: The base URL of your local LLM server (Ollama, LM Studio, etc.). Do ''not'' include `/v1/chat/completions` — it is appended automatically.

; API Key //''(optional)''//
: <$edit-text tiddler="$:/plugins/NoteStreams/WikiSage/local-llm-api-key" tag="input" default="" placeholder="leave blank if not required" />
: Only needed if your local server requires authentication.

; Supports tool calling
: <$select tiddler="$:/plugins/NoteStreams/WikiSage/local-llm-supports-tools" default="no">
<option value="yes">Yes</option>
<option value="no">No</option>
</$select>
: Set to ''Yes'' only if your local model supports OpenAI-compatible function/tool calling.

